176
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,890
no eggs remain intact.

177
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:03,670
I hope our frontline soldiers
can defend Immortal Pass to the death.

178
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,150
Hero,

179
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:13,910
