276
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:35,040
The number one madman
of the martial world,

277
00:21:35,350 --> 00:21:36,920
Crazy Yan.

278
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:41,310
Your internal energy,

279
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:44,510
